				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13416183/scp-3911#post-4701031</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2020 09:41:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I want to like this more, because I’m a big fan of occult artifacts especially when connected to the Nalka but ultimately I found this unsatisfying. The dialogue is awkward (except for the final log, quite liked that) and ultimately I don’t think the article wraps up in a satisfying way.</p> <p><em><strong>EDIT</strong></em>: I’m changing this to a plus one, I still think the MTF dialogue could use some polishing, but having read In Memoriam in order now, I have a greater appreciation for what you’re doing here. Excited to see where it goes next.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
